title: Kiss Man Person No Skin Tone Dark Skin Tone

description: Represents two men kissing, with the default skin tone for one and dark skin tone for the other. It signifies romantic love and affection between men.
apple_vendor_description: This emoji on Apple devices portrays a tender kiss between two men, with one man having a dark skin tone and the other represented without specific skin tone differentiation, focusing on the intimate gesture. The design highlights Apple's signature soft, rounded edges and subtle, realistic lighting, creating a sense of genuine affection and closeness. It's used to express romantic love, deep affection, or a loving farewell between two male partners.
